{"title":"create-chardevice","slug":"create-chardevice","date":"2019-11-15T12:16:33.000Z","updated":"2019-11-16T13:20:17.908Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/create-chardevice.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)的设计主要参考Linux Device Drives第三章-字符设备驱动程序中的scull(Simple Chararter Utility for Loading Localities)","covers":["https://i.loli.net/2019/11/15/FEtM5AmhCq1Nl8y.jpg"],"content":"<h2 id=\"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\"><a href=\"#linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux字符设备驱动设计与实现\"></a><code>linux</code>字符设备驱动设计与实现</h2><h3 id=\"TDLCD-Test-Device-For-Linux-Char-Drives-的设计\"><a href=\"#TDLCD-Test-Device-For-Linux-Char-Drives-的设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)的设计\"></a><code>TDLCD(Test Device For Linux Char Drives)</code>的设计</h3><ul>\n<li><p>主要参考<code>Linux Device Drives</code>第三章-字符设备驱动程序中的<code>scull(Simple Chararter Utility for Loading Localities)</code></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"TDLCD实现步骤\"><a href=\"#TDLCD实现步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TDLCD实现步骤\"></a><code>TDLCD</code>实现步骤</h3></li>\n<li><p>字符设备结构定义与初始化<br>定义设备结构体，并完成结构初始化函数</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>申请字符设备号<br>动态申请主、次设备号</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>完成字符设备的注册与消除函数</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>实现驱动方法</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>llseek</code>方法</li>\n<li><code>read</code>方法</li>\n<li><code>write</code>方法</li>\n<li><code>ioctl</code>方法</li>\n<li><code>open</code>方法</li>\n<li><code>release</code>方法</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"结构设计\"><a href=\"#结构设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"结构设计\"></a>结构设计</h3><h4 id=\"模块部分\"><a href=\"#模块部分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"模块部分\"></a>模块部分</h4><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h4 id=\"宏定义及头文件\"><a href=\"#宏定义及头文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"宏定义及头文件\"></a>宏定义及头文件</h4><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/module.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/init.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#define SIZE 0x1000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h4 id=\"字符设备结构设计\"><a href=\"#字符设备结构设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符设备结构设计\"></a>字符设备结构设计</h4><p>为设备定义一个结构体，包含<code>cdev</code>,私有数据及锁等相关信息。</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">tdlcd_dev</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">cdev</span> <span class=\"title\">cdev</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> mem[SIZE];</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h4 id=\"file-operations结构设计\"><a href=\"#file-operations结构设计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"file_operations结构设计\"></a><code>file_operations</code>结构设计</h4><p>将自实现的驱动方法函数传递给结构</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title\">file_operations</span> <span class=\"title\">tdlcd_fops</span>=&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    .owner=THIS_MODULE,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .llseek = tdlcd_llseek,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .read = tdlcd_read,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .write = tdlcd_write,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .unlocked_ioctl = tdlcd_ioctl,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .open = tdlcd_open,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    .release = tdlcd_release,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h4 id=\"字符设备模块的加载与卸载函数\"><a href=\"#字符设备模块的加载与卸载函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字符设备模块的加载与卸载函数\"></a>字符设备模块的加载与卸载函数</h4><ul>\n<li><p><code>static int __init tdlcd_init(void);</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>init cdev</li>\n<li>get char device number</li>\n<li>register devices</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>static void __exit tdlcd_exit(void);</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>release devices</li>\n<li>release device number</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Makefile\"><a href=\"#Makefile\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Makefile\"></a><code>Makefile</code></h3><blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">KVERS = $(shell uname -r)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># Kernel modules</span><br><span class=\"line\">obj-m += globalmem.o</span><br><span class=\"line\">obj-m += multi_globalmem.o</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># Specify flags <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> the <span class=\"keyword\">module</span> compilation.</span><br><span class=\"line\">#EXTRA_CFLAGS=-g -O0</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">build: kernel_modules</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">kernel_modules:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        make -C /lib/modules/$(KVERS)/build M=$(CURDIR) modules</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">clean:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        make -C /lib/modules/$(KVERS)/build M=$(CURDIR) clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<h3 id=\"编译装载结果\"><a href=\"#编译装载结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译装载结果\"></a>编译装载结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/15/FEtM5AmhCq1Nl8y.jpg\" alt=\"04-char-devices-compiler-insert.jpg\"></p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":5,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":3,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"}]}